data.text: @RepHalRogers @realDonaldTrump True, But an investigation is one thing; baseless claims by the sitting president do nothing but incite confusion and rage. Shame on you for perpetuating that. The president wouldn’t tell people about the severity of covid, not wanting to spread panic. This rhetoric causes panic.
@SophieGraceCha1 I know -- you explicitly said 'restitutive'. But we're human, and rage can get out of hand.
@HMittelmark And what a relief it is to complain about specifics rather than just gesturing broadly and making noises of rage!
